'''骨炭'''（Bone char），或稱'''骨黑'''（Bone black），是將動物的[[骨骼|骨頭]][[木炭|炭化]]（{{Tsl|en|charring}}）後所得到的[[炭|炭]]，為多孔隙物質。其主要成分包括了[[磷酸钙|磷酸钙]]（或[[羥磷灰石|羥磷灰石]]）57-80%、[[碳酸鈣|碳酸鈣]] 6-10%，與[[活性炭|活性炭]] 7-10%.<ref>{{cite book|last= Fawell|first=John|title=Fluoride in drinking-water|date=2006|publisher=WHO|location=Geneva|isbn=9241563192|page=47|edition=1st published.}}</ref>

==製程==
動物性骨骼經由攝氏700度[[裂解|裂解]]之後，可以得到骨炭與{{link-en|骨油|Dippel's oil}}。骨骼若在富氧環境下燃燒，則會變成[[骨灰|骨灰]]。骨炭一般原料採用牛骨，但[[颅骨|颅骨]]與[[脊椎|脊椎]]不會被使用，以避免散播[[克雅二氏病|克雅二氏病]]。<ref name="Dirty Jobs: Episode Guide">{{Cite web |url=http://dsc.discovery.com/fansites/dirtyjobs/episode/episode.html |title="Dirty Jobs: Episode Guide" |accessdate=2016-04-21 |archive-date=2011-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208105240/http://dsc.discovery.com/fansites/dirtyjobs/episode/episode.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==應用==
===水處理===
雖然骨炭具有的[[表面積|表面積]]較[[活性炭|活性炭]]為低，但足以[[吸附|吸附]]如[[12族元素|12族元素]]，包括[[铜|铜]]、[[锌|锌]]、[[镉|镉]]等重金屬。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Ko|first=Danny C.K.|author2=Porter, John F. |author3=McKay, Gordon |title=Optimised correlations for the fixed-bed adsorption of metal ions on bone char|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_chemical-engineering-science_2000-12_55_23/page/5819|journal=Chemical Engineering Science|date=December 2000|volume=55|issue=23|pages=5819–5829|doi=10.1016/S0009-2509(00)00416-4}}</ref>目前亦有研究將骨炭用於[[铅|铅]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Deydier|first=Eric|author2=Guilet, Richard |author3=Sharrock, Patrick |title=Beneficial use of meat and bone meal combustion residue: "an efficient low cost material to remove lead from aqueous effluent"|journal=Journal of Hazardous Materials|date=July 2003|volume=101|issue=1|pages=55–64|doi=10.1016/S0304-3894(03)00137-7}}</ref>與[[砷|砷]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Chen|first=Yun-Nen|author2=Chai, Li-Yuan |author3=Shu, Yu-De |title=Study of arsenic(V) adsorption on bone char from aqueous solution|journal=Journal of Hazardous Materials|date=December 2008|volume=160|issue=1|pages=168–172|doi=10.1016/j.jhazmat.2008.02.120}}</ref>之吸附與移除。

由於含有[[磷酸钙|磷酸钙]]，骨炭亦可移除[[饮水加氟|水中的氟化物]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Medellin-Castillo|first=Nahum A. |author2=Leyva-Ramos, Roberto |author3=Ocampo-Perez, Raul |author4=Garcia de la Cruz, Ramon F. |author5=Aragon-Piña, Antonio |author6=Martinez-Rosales, Jose M. |author7=Guerrero-Coronado, Rosa M. |author8=Fuentes-Rubio, Laura |title=Adsorption of Fluoride from Water Solution on Bone Char|journal=Industrial & Engineering Chemistry Research|date=December 2007|volume=46|issue=26|pages=9205–9212|doi=10.1021/ie070023n}}</ref>與金屬離子，是目前已知最早用於除去水中氟化物的方法，並曾廣泛使用於1940年代至1960年代的美國。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Horowitz|first=HS|author2=Maier, FJ |author3=Law, FE |title=Partial defluoridation of a community water supply and dental fluorosis.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_public-health-reports_1967-11_82_11/page/965|journal=Public health reports|date=Nov 1967|volume=82|issue=11|pages=965–72|pmid=4964678|pmc=1920070|doi=10.2307/4593174}}</ref>也由於骨炭原料取得容易且生產方式簡單，部分開發中國家如[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]等均仍在使用骨炭。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Mjengera|first=H.|author2=Mkongo, G.|title=Appropriate deflouridation technology for use in flourotic areas in Tanzania|journal=Physics and Chemistry of the Earth, Parts A/B/C|date=January 2003|volume=28|issue=20-27|pages=1097–1104|doi=10.1016/j.pce.2003.08.030}}</ref>

===製糖===
在[[製糖|製糖]]業上，骨炭可用來脫色與去灰分。骨炭因為其單位脫色能力較低，因此在使用時都需投入大量的骨炭以達到效果。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Asadi|first1=Mosen|title=Beet-Sugar Handbook.|date=2006|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|location=Hoboken|isbn=9780471790983|pages=333}}</ref>在美國與歐洲，由於經濟效益與素食客群和部分宗教教義之考量，因此骨炭已較少於使用在製糖業中。

除此之外，骨炭亦能去除有機雜質，尤其是[[硫酸鹽|硫酸鹽]]、[[镁|镁]]、[[钙|钙]]，有利於減少後續製程中的積垢。<ref>{{cite book|last=Chou|first=ed. by Chung Chi|title=Handbook of sugar refining : a manual for the design and operation of sugar refining facilities|date=2000|publisher=Wiley|location=New York, NY [u.a.]|isbn=9780471183570|pages=368–369}}</ref>

